snippet.textDisplay: One of my favorite I heard from you. I don't know your reasons why you stopped with the Kamelot songs, when Roy left, I tried to listen to the new stuff but I'm not getting the same feelings even though I liked Tommy a lot when they tried different singers. Roy shoes and deepness seems like unique. I even stopped listening to some for a while because I felt pain knowing that I wouldn't hear from Roy anymore (he's my favorite singer) but sometimes, things happens in life and I break my "rule" of listening to some, and so happy to have did with this video and that you did you too break your rule and record this cover. I was surprised by the female part, I'm used to your deep demon voice. Love you man, please for whatever happens in life, never stop the music :)
